OL,3,CExhibition celebrates 80 years since
OL,4,Ccity hosted Pan-African Congress
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Jahmal
OL,7,FWilliams-Thomas went along to the
OL,8,Fexhibition at Portico Library.
OL,10,FAn exhibition is celebrating 80 years
OL,11,Fsince Manchester hosted the fifth Pan-
OL,12,FAfrican Congress which changed the
OL,13,Fcourse of African history.
OL,15,FThe event was hosted over six days at
OL,16,Fthe Chorlton-on-Medlock Town Hall,
OL,17,Fwhich is now part of Manchester
OL,18,FMetropolitan University, and brought
OL,19,Ftogether African leaders to demand an
OL,20,Fend to colonial rule.
