OL,3,CExhibition celebrates 80 years since
OL,4,Ccity hosted Pan-African Congress
OL,6,FPictures and artefacts from the event,
OL,7,Fwhich took place between 15 and 21
OL,8,FOctober 1945, are now on display at
OL,9,FPortico Library.
OL,11,FWhat was the Pan African Congress?
OL,13,FPan-Africansim refers to the united
OL,14,Feffort of people of African descent to
OL,15,Fovercome racial injustice and colonial
OL,16,Foppression.
