OL,3,CExhibition celebrates 80 years since
OL,4,Ccity hosted Pan-African Congress
OL,6,FWhile the Congress in Manchester is
OL,7,Fhailed as the landmark event in
OL,8,Fchanging the course of African
OL,9,Fhistory, it was the fifth of a series
OL,10,Fof similar events.
OL,12,FThe first Pan-African Congress was
OL,13,Forganised by Trinidadian barrister
OL,14,FHenry Sylvester Williams, and was held
OL,15,Fin London in 1900, followed by similar
OL,16,Fevents in 1919, 1921 and 1923 in
OL,17,Fcities across Europe.
