OL,3,CExhibition celebrates 80 years since
OL,4,Ccity hosted Pan-African Congress
OL,6,FThe event brought together then-future
OL,7,FAfrican leaders including presidents
OL,8,Fof Malawi, Ghana and Kenya - Hastings
OL,9,FBanda, Kwame Nkrumah and Jomo Kenyatta.
OL,11,FOne of the driving forces of Nigerian
OL,12,Findependence Obafemi Awolowo was also
OL,13,Fin attendance, alongside human rights
OL,14,Fcampaigner Amy Ashwood Garvey.
OL,16,FWhy was the fifth congress held in
OL,17,FManchester?
