OL,6,FThe Pan-African movement was disrupted
OL,7,Fby global events in 1930s and didn't
OL,8,Fhold another congress until after
OL,9,FWorld War Two.
OL,11,FIt was noted that when searching for
OL,12,Fvenues, Manchester was the obvious
OL,13,Fchoice.
