OL,6,FLee-Ann Igbon with Vibrant
OL,7,FNeighbourhoods at Manchester City
OL,8,FCouncil said: "People come here to
OL,9,Fmake a difference, people come here to
OL,10,Fmake a political statement, but also
OL,11,Fit challenged racism before the Pan-
OL,12,FAfrican Congress came here to
OL,13,FManchester.
OL,15,F"Manchester still is the place to be
OL,16,Factivists and stand up for people."
